(12, 1, '2018-01-19 09:23:18', '2018-01-19 09:23:18', '[vc_row][vc_column][fancy_heading h1=\"0\" icon=\"icon-cog\" title=\"Interlab Services\"]\"Coming together is a beginning. Keeping together is a progress. Working together is a success.\"\r\nHenry Ford. [/fancy_heading][vc_column_text]The CSI promotes a culture of scientific research and Safety &amp; Security by offering interlab services such as purchase of surplus chemicals, reagent exchanges, lab safety and security waste chemicals disposal and lab audits. These services target MSc. and PhD. students undertaking research whereby we facilitate reagent exchange and disposal of waste chemicals.\r\n\r\nWe similarly advice on how to access research and analytical facilities locally and internationally. For learning and Research Institutions we carry out Lab Audits in Safety and Security, Risk Management etc.[/vc_column_text][icon_box icon=\"icon-arrows-ccw\" icon_position=\"left\" border=\"1\" title=\"Reagent Exchange\"]Due to ever increasing costs of carrying out research as well as disposal of surplus chemicals CSI provides reagent exchange services for research institutions and students. This is aimed at reducing Chemical risks associated with surplus chemicals. Similarly, this service can greatly cut down costs associated with research since some reagents are needed only in low quantities. We offer storage facility of any leftover chemicals or disposal of chemical wastes. [/icon_box][icon_box icon=\"icon-key-line\" icon_position=\"left\" border=\"1\" title=\"Equipment Access\"]Currently the number of available equipment for research is insufficient for most institutions or not available. The CSI provides access to equipment in Chemical (Analytical, Organic, Inorganic); Biological, Materials, Engineering and Environmental Research. In addition we can offer internship to students to carry out relevant research on request. [/icon_box][icon_box icon=\"icon-trash\" icon_position=\"left\" border=\"1\" title=\"Disposal of Waste Chemicals/Equipment\"]The CSI in partnership with lead agencies carries safe disposal of expired Chemicals and Equipment. This process involves collection, transportation and safe disposal of both chemicals and Equipment. [/icon_box][icon_box icon=\"icon-clipboard\" icon_position=\"left\" border=\"1\" title=\"Laboratory Audits\"]In compliance with OSHA regulations, NEMA, ISO/IEC 17025:2005, Quality Assurance and Control the CSI conducts Lab Audits for research, teaching, industrial. It compiles audit reports for purposes of internal audits and compliance requirements. [/icon_box][icon_box icon=\"icon-traffic-cone\" icon_position=\"left\" border=\"1\" title=\"Laboratory Safety and Security\"]The physical security as well as information security key requirement during research or learning in Scientific (Chemical and Biological) Laboratories. The CSI provides training service on the following:\r\n\r\n Laboratory Safety and Security\r\n Laboratory Information Management Systems\r\n Chemical Inventory Management Systems\r\n Risk Management and Mitigation etc [/icon_box][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'INTERLAB SERVICES', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'interlab-services', '', '', '2018-01-24 08:39:53', '2018-01-24 08:39:53', '', 0, 'http://localhost/csi-new/?page_id=12', 0, 'page', '', 0),
