(42, 1, '2018-01-24 08:45:17', '2018-01-24 08:45:17', '[vc_row][vc_column][fancy_heading]Insert your content here[/fancy_heading][vc_column_text]We are a Laboratory Services Provider that performs analysis of critical parameters in drinking water, agricultural soils, plants and other essential environmental tests. We offer a broad range of other services including Chemical toxicology, analytical and bioanalytical chemistry and pharmacology.\n\nThe CSI Labs has provided research and testing services to the agrochemical, water, soil, chemical, pharmaceutical, dietary supplement/functional foods, personal care, animal health, biotechnology, molecular biology and household product industries. We offer a broad range of services including Chemical toxicology, analytical and bioanalytical chemistry and pharmacology.\n\nAs a contract laboratory, CSI Labs has developed an outstanding reputation for providing excellent service, superior value and exceptional quality.\n\nWhether you require standard or customized services, our dedicated team of professionals are available to assist with the development of a research and testing program to meet your needs.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=\".vc_custom_1516608172333{margin-top: 50px !important;margin-bottom: 50px !important;}\"][vc_column][vc_custom_heading text=\"Why Choose Us?\" font_container=\"tag:h2|text_align:center\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/3\"][icon_box icon=\"icon-thermometer\" border=\"0\" title=\"Highly Interpersonal and Scientific Analytical Skills\"]We pride ourselves with highly skilled manpower in Analytical Chemistry, Soil Scientists, Agronomy, Materials Chemistry, Environmental Impact Assessment, Research and Extension skills to provide you with up to date testing and analytical skills.[/icon_box][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/3\"][icon_box icon=\"icon-doc-text\" border=\"0\" title=\"Worldwide Research Network to easily Access Equipment for Analysis\"]We have unlimited access to state of the art analytical equipment to meet client specification with regard to sampling, running experiments, data analysis and acquisition.\n[/icon_box][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/3\"][icon_box icon=\"icon-droplet\" border=\"0\" title=\"Quality Assurance and Control\"]We corroborate our results through Interlab services to enhance accuracy and precision in all our analytical works. [/icon_box][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_custom_heading text=\"Mission\" font_container=\"tag:h2|text_align:center\" css=\".vc_custom_1516626774934{margin-top: 50px !important;margin-bottom: 50px !important;}\"][vc_column_text]\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">To provide highest quality laboratory research and testing services available at a cost effective price.</p>\n\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_custom_heading text=\"Values\" font_container=\"tag:h2|text_align:center\" css=\".vc_custom_1516626875689{margin-top: 50px !important;margin-bottom: 50px !important;}\"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/4\"][vc_column_text]\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Competence &amp; Team Spirit</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n	<li>Employing a team of talented and competent staff that are experts in their field</li>\n	<li>Investing in training and creating good career opportunities</li>\n	<li>Recognizing and encouraging outstanding performance</li>\n</ul>\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/4\"][vc_column_text]\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Customer Focus</strong></h3>\n&nbsp;\n<ul>\n	<li>Delivering customer satisfaction by listening to and exceeding customer expectations</li>\n	<li>Adding value for our customers through our services</li>\n	<li>Seeking innovative solutions to help our customers achieve their goals</li>\n</ul>\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/4\"][vc_column_text]\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Quality</strong></h3>\n&nbsp;\n<ul>\n	<li>Delivering quality in all our work; providing accurate results on time</li>\n	<li>Using the best appropriate technology and methods</li>\n	<li>Seeking to improve or change our processes for the better</li>\n</ul>\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/4\"][vc_column_text]\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Integrity</strong></h3>\n&nbsp;\n<ul>\n	<li>Behaving ethically in all our business and financial activities</li>\n	<li>Demonstrating respect towards our collaborators, sponsors and our staff</li>\n	<li>Operating responsible environmental policies</li>\n</ul>\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_custom_heading text=\"Frequently Asked Questions\" font_container=\"tag:h2|text_align:center\" css=\".vc_custom_1516626862194{margin-top: 50px !important;margin-bottom: 50px !important;}\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_tta_accordion][vc_tta_section title=\"Where do I obtain my standards?\" tab_id=\"where-do-i-obtain-my-standards\"][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title=\"Do we have customized services? \" tab_id=\"do-we-have-customized-services\"][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title=\"Where are your labs based?\" tab_id=\"where-are-your-labs-based\"][/vc_tta_section][/vc_tta_accordion][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_tta_accordion][vc_tta_section title=\"What capabilities do you have?\" tab_id=\"what-capabilities-do-you-have\"][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title=\"Do you offer extension services?\" tab_id=\"do-you-offer-extension-services \"][/vc_tta_section][/vc_tta_accordion][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'ABOUT', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '8-autosave-v1', '', '', '2018-01-24 08:45:17', '2018-01-24 08:45:17', '', 8, 'http://localhost/csi-new/2018/01/22/8-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
