oals</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/4\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Quality</strong></h3>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Delivering quality in all our work; providing accurate results on time</li>\r\n	<li>Using the best appropriate technology and methods</li>\r\n	<li>Seeking to improve or change our processes for the better</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/4\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Integrity</strong></h3>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Behaving ethically in all our business and financial activities</li>\r\n	<li>Demonstrating respect towards our collaborators, sponsors and our staff</li>\r\n	<li>Operating responsible environmental policies</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_custom_heading text=\"Frequently Asked Questions\" font_container=\"tag:h2|text_align:center\" css=\".vc_custom_1516626862194{margin-top: 50px !important;margin-bottom: 50px !important;}\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_tta_accordion][vc_tta_section title=\"Where do I obtain my standards?\" tab_id=\"where-do-i-obtain-my-standards\"][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title=\"Do we have customized services? \" tab_id=\"do-we-have-customized-services\"][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title=\"Where are your labs based?\" tab_id=\"where-are-your-labs-based\"][/vc_tta_section][/vc_tta_accordion][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_tta_accordion][vc_tta_section title=\"What capabilities do you have?\" tab_id=\"what-capabilities-do-you-have\"][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title=\"Do you offer extension services?\" tab_id=\"do-you-offer-extension-services \"][/vc_tta_section][/vc_tta_accordion][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'ABOUT', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '8-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-01-22 13:14:39', '2018-01-22 13:14:39', '', 8, 'ht