(66, 1, '2018-01-24 09:20:21', '2018-01-24 09:20:21', '[vc_row][vc_column][fancy_heading h1=\"0\" icon=\"icon-cog\" title=\"Our Services\"]We offer unrivaled services encompassing state of the art technology to guarantee results. [/fancy_heading][vc_custom_heading text=\"Research and Development Quality Assurance.\"][vc_column_text]Since the inception of CSI International, we strive to constantly offer efficient, reliable and customized services to client needs. We continue to improve and expanding our services to meet client needs through customer feedback.\n\nAll our staff are professionally trained and have a wealth of experience and knowledge in Research and Development including: sampling, testing, data analysis and acquisition to provide accurate and timely results to our clients.\n\nOur staff comprise of member with qualifications ranging from HND, BSc., MSc. and PhD in Physical Chemistry, Biological, Environmental and Agricultural Sciences.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_custom_heading text=\"Our Services\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/3\"][icon_box icon=\"\" border=\"1\" title=\"Water Analysis\" image=\"67\"]Our staff performs water testing for inorganic and volatile organic compounds for drinking, domestic and waste water. We have instrumentation dedicated to water testing and test for all the regulated and non-regulated compounds of concern. Our Labs carry out a wider range of analyses relevant to the health related parameters laid down by WHO water quality standards.[/icon_box][vc_btn title=\"Learn more\" color=\"success\" align=\"center\" link=\"url:http%3A%2F%2Flocalhost%2Fcsi-new%2Fwater-analysis%2F|||\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/3\"][icon_box icon=\"\" border=\"1\" title=\"Soil Sampling and Analysis\" image=\"69\"]We offer chemical and mechanical analysis of soils for variety of uses. Our mission is to provide accurate and timely soil test reports to meet the unique agricultural and environmental needs of our country. We provide information on techniques of soil sampling and carry out various analyses on agricultural soil. \n\n[/icon_box][vc_btn title=\"Learn more\" color=\"success\" align=\"center\" link=\"url:http%3A%2F%2Flocalhost%2Fcsi-new%2Fsoil-sampling-and-analysis%2F|||\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/3\"][icon_box icon=\"\" border=\"0\" title=\"Agrochemicals/Pesticide Residue Analysis\" image=\"71\"]Agriculture farming such as Horticulture and Floriculture relies heavily on use of farm inputs such as agrochemicals, pesticides and fertilizers. In pesticide analysis we determine levels of remnant residues of pesticides in food and soils. This in important for the consumers to be assured of the quality and level of residues within food. [/icon_box][vc_btn title=\"Learn more\" color=\"success\" align=\"center\" link=\"url:http%3A%2F%2Flocalhost%2Fcsi-new%2Fagrochemicals-pesticide-residue-analysis%2F|||\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/3\"][icon_box icon=\"\" border=\"1\" title=\"Research & Data Analysis\" image=\"72\"]We offer unrivalled, professional research lab testing services and data analysis for companies, institutions and students undertaking research. Be it for your graduate or post graduate degree, we have you covered. We offer direct research in the following fields:[/icon_box][vc_btn title=\"Learn more\" color=\"success\" align=\"center\" link=\"url:http%3A%2F%2Flocalhost%2Fcsi-new%2Fresearch-data-analysis%2F|||\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/3\"][icon_box icon=\"\" border=\"1\" title=\"Solid State and Materials Analysis\" image=\"68\"]Currently in Kenya we have advanced materials research in the field of materials attributed to growing demand for building materials, Road Construction materials, Engineering Materials, Manufacturing materials and Mineralogy. Our Laboratories have the capacity to perform...[/icon_box][vc_btn title=\"Learn more\" color=\"success\" align=\"center\" link=\"url:http%3A%2F%2Flocalhost%2Fcsi-new%2Fsolid-state-and-materials-analysis%2F|||\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/3\"][icon_box icon=\"\" border=\"0\" title=\"Environmental Impact Assessment and Audit\" image=\"70\"]We perform Environmental Impact Assessment to identify and predict the impact of a project or programmes on the bio-geophysical environment and on man\'s health and well-being, to interpret...[/icon_box][vc_btn title=\"Learn more\" color=\"success\" align=\"center\" link=\"url:http%3A%2F%2Flocalhost%2Fcsi-new%2Fenvironmental-impact-assessment-and-audit%2F|||\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/3\"][icon_box icon=\"\" border=\"1\" title=\"Research & Data Analysis\" image=\"72\"]We offer unrivalled, professional research lab testing services and data analysis for companies, institutions and students undertaking research. Be it for your graduate or post graduate degree, we have you covered. We offer direct research in the following fields:[/icon_box][vc_btn title=\"Learn more\" color=\"success\" align=\"center\" link=\"url:http%3A%2F%2Flocalhost%2Fcsi-new%2Fresearch-data-analysis%2F|||\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/3\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/3\"][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'SERVICES', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '10-autosave-v1', '', '', '2018-01-24 09:20:21', '2018-01-24 09:20:21', '', 10, 'http://localhost/csi-new/2018/01/24/10-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
