(84, 1, '2018-01-24 06:34:27', '2018-01-24 06:34:27', '[vc_row][vc_column][vc_single_image image=\"108\" img_size=\"full\" alignment=\"center\"][vc_custom_heading text=\"Soil Sampling and Analysis\"][vc_column_text]We offer chemical and mechanical analysis of soils for variety of uses. Our mission is to provide accurate and timely soil test reports to meet the unique agricultural and environmental needs of our country. We provide information on techniques of soil sampling and carry out various analyses on agricultural soil. Our services comprises of:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Collection of a representative soil sample</li>\r\n 	<li>Laboratory analyses of the soil sample</li>\r\n 	<li>Interpretation of analytical results</li>\r\n 	<li>Management recommendations based on interpreted analytical results</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nIn soil analysis we determine physical conditions, fertility (nutrient) status, and chemical properties that affect their suitability as plant growing media. Examples of parameters that are analyzed in our labs are:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Soil pH</li>\r\n 	<li>Electrical conductivity</li>\r\n 	<li>Organic matter</li>\r\n 	<li>Micronutrients Essential trace elements</li>\r\n 	<li>Heavy metals such as lead, cadmium, arsenic, mercury etc.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Soil Sampling and Analysis', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'soil-sampling-and-analysis', '', '', '2018-01-24 06:58:53', '2018-01-24 06:58:53', '', 0, 'http://localhost/csi-new/?page_id=84', 0, 'page', '', 0),
