(86, 1, '2018-01-24 06:34:55', '2018-01-24 06:34:55', '[vc_row][vc_column][vc_single_image image=\"97\" img_size=\"full\" alignment=\"center\"][vc_custom_heading text=\"Agrochemicals/Pesticide Residue Analysis\"][vc_column_text]Agriculture farming such as Horticulture and Floriculture relies heavily on use of farm inputs such as agrochemicals, pesticides and fertilizers. In pesticide analysis we determine levels of remnant residues of pesticides in food and soils. This in important for the consumers to be assured of the quality and level of residues within food. Similarly organic farming that does not utilize artificial farm inputs would benefit from our pesticide residue analysis. Services offered during pesticide analysis include:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Sampling/Sample Collection</li>\r\n 	<li>Extraction</li>\r\n 	<li>Determination: GC-MS; LC-MS; HPLC-UV etc</li>\r\n 	<li>Data Acquisition and evaluation</li>\r\n 	<li>Quantification</li>\r\n 	<li>Reporting</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nWe also provide advice on the following:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Integrated Pest Management</li>\r\n 	<li>Safe Use of Pesticides</li>\r\n 	<li>Pesticide Resistance</li>\r\n 	<li>Disposal and Storage of Pesticides</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Agrochemicals/Pesticide Residue Analysis', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'agrochemicals-pesticide-residue-analysis', '', '', '2018-01-24 06:48:56', '2018-01-24 06:48:56', '', 0, 'http://localhost/csi-new/?page_id=86', 0, 'page', '', 0),
