(89, 1, '2018-01-24 06:35:29', '2018-01-24 06:35:29', '[vc_row][vc_column][vc_single_image image=\"105\" img_size=\"full\" alignment=\"center\"][vc_custom_heading text=\"Research &amp; Data Analysis\"][vc_column_text]We offer unrivaled, professional research lab testing services and data analysis for companies, institutions and students undertaking research. Be it for your graduate or post graduate degree, we have you covered. We offer direct research in the following fields:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Environmental Quality Assessment such as one required by National Environmental Management Authority (NEMA)</li>\r\n 	<li>Water Quality Testing</li>\r\n 	<li>Soil and Solid Wastes Analysis</li>\r\n 	<li>Mineral Prospecting and Analysis</li>\r\n 	<li>Petroleum and Petrochemical Analysis</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nThrough data analysis, we shall enable you understand the data analysis procedures which will help you to:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Appreciate the scientific methods, hypotheses testing and statistical significance in relation to your research questions.</li>\r\n 	<li>Realise the importance of good research design when investigating research questions</li>\r\n 	<li>Be able to devise, implement and report accurately small quantitative research project</li>\r\n 	<li>Be capable of identifying the data analysis procedures relevant to your research project.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Research & Data Analysis', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'research-data-analysis', '', '', '2018-01-24 06:55:13', '2018-01-24 06:55:13', '', 0, 'http://localhost/csi-new/?page_id=89', 0, 'page', '', 0),
