(92, 1, '2018-01-24 06:35:57', '2018-01-24 06:35:57', '[vc_row][vc_column][vc_single_image image=\"111\" img_size=\"full\" alignment=\"center\"][vc_custom_heading text=\"Solid State and Materials Analysis\"][vc_column_text]Currently in Kenya we have advanced materials research in the field of materials attributed to growing demand for building materials, Road Construction materials, Engineering Materials, Manufacturing materials and Mineralogy. Our Laboratories have the capacity to perform tests on solid materials for structure, elemental composition, purity, Confirmatory tests and morphology. Through partnership we can provide the following solid state analytical services and data interpretation:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>X-ray Diffraction (XRD) analysis</li>\r\n 	<li>Energy Dispersive Spectroscopy /X-ray Photoelectron Spectroscopy Analysis</li>\r\n 	<li>Scanning Electron Microscopy</li>\r\n 	<li>Transmission Electron Microscopy</li>\r\n 	<li>Surface Area Analysis (BET)</li>\r\n 	<li>Solid State NMR</li>\r\n 	<li>Mechanical testing eg. Stress, Strain, Tensile, torsion etc</li>\r\n 	<li>Electrical Conductivity</li>\r\n 	<li>Elemental Composition using Elemental Analyzer</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Solid State and Materials Analysis', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'solid-state-and-materials-analysis', '', '', '2018-01-24 07:01:46', '2018-01-24 07:01:46', '', 0, 'http://localhost/csi-new/?page_id=92', 0, 'page', '', 0),
