(94, 1, '2018-01-24 06:36:23', '2018-01-24 06:36:23', '[vc_row][vc_column][vc_single_image image=\"100\" img_size=\"full\" alignment=\"center\"][vc_custom_heading text=\"Environmental Impact Assessment and Audit\"][vc_column_text]We perform Environmental Impact Assessment to identify and predict the impact of a project or programmes on the bio-geophysical environment and on man\'s health and well-being, to interpret and communicate information about the impact, to analyze site and process alternatives and provide solutions to sift out, or abate/mitigate the negative consequences on man and the environment.\r\n\r\nWe perform environmental audit to assess the compliance of environmental administration and performance of an operating business with environmental protection requirements, with sound environmental practice in general, and with the principles of sustainable development. Environmental auditing is mandatory only in cases stipulated by law.\r\n\r\nOur environmental audit is a systematic, independent review to check whether the results of environmental work tally with the targets. It similarly focuses on whether the methods used to achieve goals are effective.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Environmental Impact Assessment and Audit', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'environmental-impact-assessment-and-audit', '', '', '2018-01-24 06:46:45', '2018-01-24 06:46:45', '', 0, 'http://localhost/csi-new/?page_id=94', 0, 'page', '', 0),
