(109, 1, '2018-01-24 06:58:53', '2018-01-24 06:58:53', '[vc_row][vc_column][vc_single_image image=\"108\" img_size=\"full\" alignment=\"center\"][vc_custom_heading text=\"Soil Sampling and Analysis\"][vc_column_text]We offer chemical and mechanical analysis of soils for variety of uses. Our mission is to provide accurate and timely soil test reports to meet the unique agricultural and environmental needs of our country. We provide information on techniques of soil sampling and carry out various analyses on agricultural soil. Our services comprises of:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Collection of a representative soil sample</li>\r\n 	<li>Laboratory analyses of the soil sample</li>\r\n 	<li>Interpretation of analytical results</li>\r\n 	<li>Management recommendations based on interpreted analytical results</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nIn soil analysis we determine physical conditions, fertility (nutrient) status, and chemical properties that affect their suitability as plant growing media. Examples of parameters that are analyzed in our labs are:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Soil pH</li>\r\n 	<li>Electrical conductivity</li>\r\n 	<li>Organic matter</li>\r\n 	<li>Micronutrients Essential trace elements</li>\r\n 	<li>Heavy metals such as lead, cadmium, arsenic, mercury etc.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Soil Sampling and Analysis', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '84-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-01-24 06:58:53', '2018-01-24 06:58:53', '', 84, 'http://localhost/csi-new/2018/01/24/84-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(110, 1, '2018-01-24 07:01:21', '2018-01-24 07:01:21', '[vc_row][vc_column][vc_single_image][vc_custom_heading text=\"Solid State and Materials Analysis\"][vc_column_text]Currently in Kenya we have advanced materials research in the field of materials attributed to growing demand for building materials, Road Construction materials, Engineering Materials, Manufacturing materials and Mineralogy. Our Laboratories have the capacity to perform tests on solid materials for structure, elemental composition, purity, Confirmatory tests and morphology. Through partnership we can provide the following solid state analytical services and data interpretation:\n<ul>\n 	<li>X-ray Diffraction (XRD) analysis</li>\n 	<li>Energy Dispersive Spectroscopy /X-ray Photoelectron Spectroscopy Analysis</li>\n 	<li>Scanning Electron Microscopy</li>\n 	<li>Transmission Electron Microscopy</li>\n 	<li>Surface Area Analysis (BET)</li>\n 	<li>Solid State NMR</li>\n 	<li>Mechanical testing eg. Stress, Strain, Tensile, torsion etc</li>\n 	<li>Electrical Conductivity</li>\n 	<li>Elemental Composition using Elemental Analyzer</li>\n</ul>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]<span style=\"display: inline-block; width: 0px; overflow: hidden; line-height: 0;\" data-mce-type=\"bookmark\" class=\"mce_SELRES_start\"></span>', 'Solid State and Materials Analysis', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '92-autosave-v1', '', '', '2018-01-24 07:01:21', '2018-01-24 07:01:21', '', 92, 'http://localhost/csi-new/2018/01/24/92-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
