(131, 1, '2018-01-24 08:42:26', '2018-01-24 08:42:26', '[vc_row][vc_column][fancy_heading h1=\"0\" icon=\"icon-cog\" title=\"Our Services\"]We offer unrivaled services encompassing state of the art technology to guarantee results. [/fancy_heading][vc_column_text]Since the inception of CSI International, we strive to constantly offer efficient, reliable and customized services to client needs. We continue to improve and expanding our services to meet client needs through customer feedback.\r\n\r\nAll our staff are professionally trained and have a wealth of experience and knowledge in Research and Development including: sampling, testing, data analysis and acquisition to provide accurate and timely results to our clients.\r\n\r\nOur staff comprise of member with qualifications ranging from HND, BSc., MSc. and PhD in Physical Chemistry, Biological, Environmental and Agricultural Sciences.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_custom_heading text=\"Our Services\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/3\"][icon_box icon=\"\" border=\"1\" title=\"Water Analysis\" image=\"67\"]Our staff performs water testing for inorganic and volatile organic compounds for drinking, domestic and waste water. We have instrumentation dedicated to water testing and test for all the regulated and non-regulated compounds of concern. Our Labs carry out a wider range of analyses relevant to the health related parameters laid down by WHO water quality standards.[/icon_box][vc_btn title=\"Learn more\" color=\"success\" align=\"center\" link=\"url:http%3A%2F%2Flocalhost%2Fcsi-new%2Fwater-analysis%2F|||\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/3\"][icon_box icon=\"\" border=\"1\" title=\"Soil Sampling and Analysis\" image=\"69\"]We offer chemical and mechanical analysis of soils for variety of uses. Our mission is to provide accurate and timely soil test reports to meet the unique agricultural and environmental needs of our country. We provide information on techniques o