column][vc_column width=\"1/3\"][icon_box icon=\"\" border=\"0\" title=\"Environmental Impact Assessment and Audit\" image=\"70\"]We perform Environmental Impact Assessment to identify and predict the impact of a project or programmes on the bio-geophysical environment and on man\'s health and well-being, to interpret...[/icon_box][vc_btn title=\"Learn more\" color=\"success\" align=\"center\" link=\"url:http%3A%2F%2Flocalhost%2Fcsi-new%2Fenvironmental-impact-assessment-and-audit%2F|||\"][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'SERVICES', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '10-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-01-24 08:42:26', '2018-01-24 08:42:26', '', 10, 'http://localhost/csi-new/2018/01/24/10-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
